						<summary>

						<p>On a large hero-stone standing in the ruined Saṅgamēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 12th century.</p>						

						<p>This seems to describe the death of a hero in a fight. It seems to mention the warrior <hi rend="italic">Tantrapāḷa</hi> Karṇa. The inscription is much damaged.</p>						

